,Recommended,221180,14777904,"Posted: 7 March, 2015",all,Robson,"This game came out several years ago and recently got a HD upgrade. Unlike most games, anyone who owned the original got the HD version for free. That’s always appreciated.It’s a semi-relaxing puzzle/RTS game where you have various planet-like structures, surrounded by your seedlings. These seedlings can move to different planets and turn into trees, which are used to make more seedlings or to work as defences. The idea of most levels is to have as many seedlings as possible and attack other planets to take over the sector. It is constantly introducing new game mechanics, so it’s always interesting. The levels sometimes have different objectives (get to here, protect this planet, rescue these seedlings, etc) to provide variety.It’s also pretty awesome for playing whilst watching something (TV, YouTube, etc). Alternatively, if you just want to play the game, you can increase the speed."
