,Recommended,221180,34597401,Posted: 29 August,all,Deth Invictus,"This is a fun little game and will chew up your free time if you let it.  Supposedly relaxing but can be quite hectic on some levels.There is one major flaw in this game - one of the achievements is impossible.  The ""Hero"" achievement is broken.  Level 12 is supposed to have 100 seedlings you can find/rescue on the map (on top of your starting 100).  There are only 60.  The devs acknowledged this issue and promised a fix several years ago.  It has not eventuated.As I am an achievement hunter, this ruins the game for me completely.Game is 9.5 out of 10 for me for just the game but, due to the broken achievement which makes it impossible to get a perfect completion in Steam, I cannot recommend this game to anybody with any level of achievement OCD.EDIT:  I found that there are LUA files for each level.  I modified the LUA file for level 12 so that it no longer has only 60 seedlings to rescue.  This allowed me to complete the ""Hero"" achievement for the game.  Note that, even with that adjustment, there are actually too few seedlings to rescue to make the achievement possible (adding the extra 40 was not enough) so adjust the numbers accordingly and the achievement will unlock.  I am amending my recommendation based on my discovery and completion of the game."
