,Recommended,221180,35319312,Posted: 29 September,all,@nthon,"Amusing little mosquito simulator.The game is a small conquer the islands type of game where you take over the asteroids with seedlings. Seedlings have stats depends on which asteroid they were grown on, and as a result are faster, stronger or hit harder than other spawns.To expand your asteroid empire, you plant offensive or defensive trees, resulting in a SAMsite tree or a spawner tree. Later on you end up having randomly spawning flowers which can buff your trees to grow a laser mine or turn your seedlings into steroid mosquitos.The campaign usually has a little twist, though it eventually comes down to the same, mass a big army of strong death needles by expanding your asteroids you hold and steamrolling the rest. There are a few missions with a twist though, like a hide and seek one (though the AI doesn't play by the challenge's rules at times and ruins your day, play on the relaxed mode for a fairer fight on that one).I can recommend it provided not playing it too much consecutively, then you do feel your'e just doing the same over and over.Enjoy it for its relatively calm gameplay, and steroid mosquito simulation."
